  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425320/extras/20acf2e7c1daa52c92a43a74b59acd66.poster.avif?t=1768985442\" width=480 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425320/extras/20acf2e7c1daa52c92a43a74b59acd66.webm?t=1768985442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425320/extras/20acf2e7c1daa52c92a43a74b59acd66.mp4?t=1768985442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Another action-packed crime romp from the infamous PAKO series!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PAKO 4 is an atmospheric and violent indie action game where the player causes chaos in a big city by committing crimes with his accomplice and escaping the police. You can move around the city on foot or by car. Fast-paced arcade gameplay from PAKO 2 meets more in depth looting mechanics in the North Paw area! Come and enjoy the old school feel of doing crimes!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425320/extras/ce8f6ba11c1ff159ce8211f94ea95c0e.webp?t=1768985442\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425320/extras/ce8f6ba11c1ff159ce8211f94ea95c0e.poster.webp?t=1768985442\" class=\"bb_img\" width=320 height=180 /></picture></span><br><br>Key features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single-player action game: drive and walk freely around in the city</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Loot money within a time limit and escape</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro inspired graphics of the early 2000s games we all loved!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hire crew members with different bonus effects </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If your car breaks down, keep escaping on foot and take another: every car is drivable!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot twin-stick style and destroy stuff!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game radio channels bringing the bangers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take screenshots in Photo Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425320/extras/fbb821ead7c6ef17fc700b70f8759d37.poster.avif?t=1768985442\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425320/extras/fbb821ead7c6ef17fc700b70f8759d37.webm?t=1768985442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425320/extras/fbb821ead7c6ef17fc700b70f8759d37.mp4?t=1768985442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425320/extras/20acf2e7c1daa52c92a43a74b59acd66.poster.avif?t=1768985442\" width=480 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425320/extras/20acf2e7c1daa52c92a43a74b59acd66.webm?t=1768985442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425320/extras/20acf2e7c1daa52c92a43a74b59acd66.mp4?t=1768985442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Another action-packed crime romp from the infamous PAKO series!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PAKO 4 is an atmospheric and violent indie action game where the player causes chaos in a big city by committing crimes with his accomplice and escaping the police. You can move around the city on foot or by car. Fast-paced arcade gameplay from PAKO 2 meets more in depth looting mechanics in the North Paw area! Come and enjoy the old school feel of doing crimes!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425320/extras/ce8f6ba11c1ff159ce8211f94ea95c0e.webp?t=1768985442\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425320/extras/ce8f6ba11c1ff159ce8211f94ea95c0e.poster.webp?t=1768985442\" class=\"bb_img\" width=320 height=180 /></picture></span><br><br>Key features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Single-player action game: drive and walk freely around in the city</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Loot money within a time limit and escape</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro inspired graphics of the early 2000s games we all loved!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hire crew members with different bonus effects </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If your car breaks down, keep escaping on foot and take another: every car is drivable!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot twin-stick style and destroy stuff!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In-game radio channels bringing the bangers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take screenshots in Photo Mode</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425320/extras/fbb821ead7c6ef17fc700b70f8759d37.poster.avif?t=1768985442\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425320/extras/fbb821ead7c6ef17fc700b70f8759d37.webm?t=1768985442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3425320/extras/fbb821ead7c6ef17fc700b70f8759d37.mp4?t=1768985442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
